$$
\boxed{\begin{pmatrix} P_{on}(t) \\ P_{off}(t) \end{pmatrix} = \begin{pmatrix} \frac{k_{on}}{k_{on} + k_{off}} + \left(p_{0} - \frac{k_{on}}{k_{on} + k_{off}}\right) \exp\left(-(k_{on} + k_{off})t\right) \\ \frac{k_{off}}{k_{on} + k_{off}} + \left(1 - p_{0} - \frac{k_{off}}{k_{on} + k_{off}}\right) \exp\left(-(k_{on} + k_{off})t\right) \end{pmatrix}}
$$
